Hide unnecessary Source Control UI elements

Strip the Source Control view down to only show the changed files list.
Customers should not be able to stage, commit, or see the commit graph.
This hides the commit message input, action buttons, inline stage/unstage
actions, provider toolbar actions, and removes the Graph view entirely.

